  "prompt": "Where can I search for best five star hotel in Bhopal?",
  "response": "To find the best five-star hotels in Bhopal, you can explore several resources online:\n\n1. **Travel Websites**: Websites like TripAdvisor, Booking.com, Expedia, and Agoda allow you to filter hotels by star rating and read user reviews. You can also see ratings, prices, and amenities.\n\n2. **Google Search**: Simply searching \"best five-star hotels in Bhopal\" on Google will yield a list of hotels along with reviews and ratings. Google Maps can also show locations and user feedback.\n\n3. **Hotel Aggregator Apps**: Mobile apps like Hotels.com, Trivago, or Oyo can help you compare prices and read reviews from various platforms.\n\n4. **Social Media and Travel Blogs**: Instagram, Facebook, and travel blogs often showcase hotels with stunning photos and personal experiences.\n\n5. **Local Travel Agencies**: If you prefer personalized assistance, local travel agencies can provide recommendations based on your preferences.\n\nMake sure to check recent reviews and ratings to ensure the quality of the hotel meets your expectations.",
